f=\"/index.php/House_Mooton\" title=\"House Mooton\">Mooton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Nutt\" title=\"House Nutt\">Nutt</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Perryn\" title=\"House Perryn\">Perryn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Piper\" title=\"House Piper\">Piper</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Roote\" title=\"House Roote\">Roote</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Shawney\" title=\"House Shawney\">Shawney</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Smallwood\" title=\"House Smallwood\">Smallwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Atranta\" title=\"House Vance of Atranta\">Vance of Atranta</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest\" title=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest\">Vance of Wayfarer's Rest</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vypren\" title=\"House Vypren\">Vypren</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wayn\" title=\"House Wayn\">Wayn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Whent\" title=\"House Whent\">Whent</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Knightly Houses</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Cox\" title=\"House Cox\">Cox</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Paege\" title=\"House Paege\">Paege</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wode\" title=\"House Wode\">Wode</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Other Houses<br /><small>(noble rank unknown)</small></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blanetree\" title=\"House Blanetree\">Blanetree</a>